<subSubSection id="C337088DF77AB13BB182FD043033401F" pageId="15" pageNumber="536" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F77AB13BB182FD043033401F" blockId="15.[151,1437,223,862]" pageId="15" pageNumber="536">
COMMENTS: Date and place agree with the journal entries. 
<typeStatus id="5496E5A4F77AB13BB20AFD0331BE4054" box="[847,903,764,790]" pageId="15" pageNumber="536">Type</typeStatus>
locality (erroneously) corrected to Hammanskraal by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFBC26F7F77AB13BB1A9FCE03028407B" author="Gyldenstolpe, N." box="[236,529,799,825]" pageId="15" pageNumber="536" pagination="264 - 292" refId="ref28785" refString="Gyldenstolpe, N. (1934) The travels and collections of Johan August Wahlberg, 1810 - 1856: a pioneer naturalist in South Africa. Ibis, 76, 264 - 292. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1474 - 919 X. 1934. tb 01567. x" type="journal article" year="1934">Gyldenstolpe (1934: 292)</bibRefCitation>
. Wahlberg’s journal does not have an entry for 
<date id="FF937DC6F77AB13BB562FCDF36F1407B" box="[1063,1224,799,826]" pageId="15" pageNumber="536" value="1842-03-07">7 March 1842</date>
, but from 6 March to 9 April he camped at Tswaing.
</paragraph>
